duties_responsibilities.duty: Receive, ship, and maintain inventory levels for finished goods and other items, including international shipments.
Process SAP business system transactions daily to support production, receiving, and shipping transactions.
Run audit reports from SAP to identify/verify errors for inbound & outbound shipments.
Maintain FIFO inventory management practice and perform cycle count process.
Create shipping labels and recordkeeping of paperwork including bills of lading, packing lists, and incoming goods receipts.
Verify, process, and put away incoming purchase orders.
